Final Exam

The final exam for this course will occur in our class Moodle shell. The exam will be open between 9:00am - 11:00am PT, on Tuesday, August 8th. You will need to begin the exam by 11:15am PT. Please allow 45 minutes to complete the exam. There is an abstract available on our class website. Please print the abstract and have it available for a reference during the final exam.

The exam is comprised of 32 multiple choice questions.Â  The exam content is similar to the quizzes in the Northwestern Health Sciences University online EIP modules.
